task.summary: Implement CacheBehavior for IBaseQueryRequest and ICacheableQuery with param-based cache keys - Added CacheBehavior<TRequest, TResponse> pipeline behavior for queries - Cache key generated dynamically using query type and CacheKeyParams - Handler executed if cache miss occurs, response serialized and cached - Supports any TResponse type via JSON serialization - Applies only to queries implementing IBaseQueryRequest and ICacheableQuery
